title: Authorities checking if 2 asthma deaths in GenSan linked to haze
text:
Authorities checking if 2 asthma deaths in GenSan linked to haze 
GMA News Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Air sampler equipment are used to measure the quality of air in a particular area, according to the report. Meanwhile the local arm of the Health department in Davao City said that the air quality there is not hazardous yet. In Visayas, on the other hand, all flights on Saturday in Bohol province were canceled due to the thick haze that hamper safe air navigation....
